Forensic Defence & Legal Advisory


“Scientific clarity when it matters most.”

Independent forensic review and litigation-focused advisory services for defence teams, prosecutors, judicial authorities, and oversight bodies.

We provide objective evaluation of:
	•	Laboratory compliance and accreditation status
	•	Method validation and interpretation reliability
	•	DNA mixture analysis and uncertainty application
	•	Chain-of-custody integrity
	•	Digital forensic tool validation
